Short Description

Learned and practiced MySQL string functions (TRIM(), LTRIM(), RTRIM()) to remove unwanted spaces and clean text data.

README Description
# Day X - MySQL String Functions

Today's practice focused on string manipulation functions in MySQL.

## Topics Covered
- TRIM()
- LTRIM()
- RTRIM()

## Sample Queries

```sql
SELECT TRIM('   hello   ');
SELECT LTRIM('   hello hello   ');
SELECT RTRIM('hello hello   ');
SELECT TRIM('*' FROM '***hello***');
Key Takeaway

Even extra spaces matter! These functions help clean and format text data efficiently.


